@startuml
title Sequence - Create Employee
actor Admin as "HR Admin"
boundary UI as "Admin UI"
control API as "Admin API"
entity EmployeeService
database DB as "Admin Database"
participant Mail as "Email Service"

Admin -> UI : Mở form thêm nhân viên
UI -> API : Gửi dữ liệu nhân viên
API -> EmployeeService : validate payload
EmployeeService -> DB : check duplicate email
DB --> EmployeeService : result

alt Email exists
  EmployeeService --> API : validation error
  API --> UI : Hiển thị lỗi email đã tồn tại
else Valid
  EmployeeService -> DB : create employee
  DB --> EmployeeService : created
  EmployeeService -> Mail : send welcome email
  Mail --> EmployeeService : sent
  EmployeeService --> API : success
  API --> UI : Trả kết quả tạo thành công
  UI --> Admin : Hiển thị thông báo thành công
end

@enduml
